results.description:
White Rock lake, lower spillway steps
My Eyes Match The Leaves
Baby black-crowned night herons start out with yellow eyes then gradually transition to the red eyes of an adult as they grow up.  This juvenile is about halfway thru the transition and had amazing orange eyes that matched the leaves surrounding it.
